{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"Over the last 13 years --"},{"time":2000,"text":"one, three, 13 years --"},{"time":4000,"text":"I've been part of an exceptional team at InSightec in Israel"},{"time":7000,"text":"and partners around the world"},{"time":9000,"text":"for taking this idea, this concept,"},{"time":12000,"text":"noninvasive surgery,"},{"time":14000,"text":"from the research lab to routine clinical use."},{"time":17000,"text":"And this is what I'll tell you about."},{"time":19000,"text":"13 years --"},{"time":21000,"text":"for some of you, you can empathize with that number."},{"time":24000,"text":"For me, today, on this date,"},{"time":26000,"text":"it's like a second bar mitzvah experience."}]},{"cues":[{"time":28000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":31000,"text":"So this dream"},{"time":34000,"text":"is really enabled"},{"time":36000,"text":"by the convergence"},{"time":38000,"text":"of two known technologies."},{"time":40000,"text":"One is the focused ultrasound,"},{"time":42000,"text":"and the other one is the"},{"time":45000,"text":"vision-enabled magnetic resonance imaging."},{"time":48000,"text":"So let's first talk about focused ultrasound."},{"time":52000,"text":"And I hold in my hand"},{"time":54000,"text":"a tissue-mimicking phantom."},{"time":56000,"text":"It is made out of silicon."},{"time":58000,"text":"It is transparent, made just for you."},{"time":61000,"text":"So you see, it's all intact,"},{"time":64000,"text":"completely transparent."},{"time":66000,"text":"I'll take you now to the acoustic lab."},{"time":69000,"text":"You see the phantom within the aquarium."},{"time":71000,"text":"This is a setup I put in a physics lab."},{"time":73000,"text":"On the right-hand side,"},{"time":75000,"text":"you see an ultrasonic transducer."},{"time":77000,"text":"So the ultrasonic transducer"},{"time":80000,"text":"emits basically an ultrasonic beam"},{"time":82000,"text":"that focuses inside the phantom."},{"time":85000,"text":"Okay, when you hear the click,"},{"time":89000,"text":"this is when the energy starts to emit"},{"time":91000,"text":"and you see a little lesion form"},{"time":94000,"text":"inside the phantom."},{"time":97000,"text":"Okay, so everything around it"},{"time":99000,"text":"is whole and intact."},{"time":101000,"text":"It's just a lesion formed inside."},{"time":103000,"text":"So think about, this is in your brain."},{"time":106000,"text":"We need to reach a target inside the brain."},{"time":108000,"text":"We can do it without harming any tissue."},{"time":111000,"text":"So this is, I think,"},{"time":113000,"text":"the first kosher Hippocratic surgical system."}]},{"cues":[{"time":116000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":118000,"text":"Okay, so let's talk a little bit about ultrasound,"},{"time":120000,"text":"the force of ultrasound."},{"time":122000,"text":"You know all about imaging, right, ultrasound imaging."},{"time":125000,"text":"And you know also about lithotripsy --"},{"time":128000,"text":"breaking kidney stones."},{"time":131000,"text":"But ultrasound can be shaped"},{"time":134000,"text":"to be anything in between,"},{"time":137000,"text":"because it's a mechanical force."},{"time":140000,"text":"Basically, it's a force acting on a tissue"},{"time":142000,"text":"that it transverses."},{"time":144000,"text":"So you can change the intensity, the frequency,"},{"time":147000,"text":"the duration, the pulse shape of the ultrasound"},{"time":150000,"text":"to create anything"},{"time":152000,"text":"from an airbrush to a hammer."},{"time":155000,"text":"And I am going to show you"},{"time":157000,"text":"multiple applications in the medical field"},{"time":159000,"text":"that can be enabled"},{"time":161000,"text":"just by focusing,"},{"time":163000,"text":"physically focusing."}]},{"cues":[{"time":166000,"text":"So this idea"},{"time":168000,"text":"of harnessing focused ultrasound to treat lesions in the brain"},{"time":171000,"text":"is not new at all."},{"time":173000,"text":"When I was born, this idea was already conceived"},{"time":176000,"text":"by pioneers such as the Fry brothers"},{"time":179000,"text":"and Lars Leksell,"},{"time":181000,"text":"who is know actually"},{"time":183000,"text":"as the inventor of the gammaknife."},{"time":185000,"text":"But you may not know"},{"time":187000,"text":"that he tried to perform lobotomies in the brain,"},{"time":189000,"text":"noninvasively,"},{"time":191000,"text":"with focused ultrasound in the '50s."},{"time":194000,"text":"He failed,"},{"time":196000,"text":"so he then invented the gammaknife."},{"time":198000,"text":"And it makes you ponder"},{"time":201000,"text":"why those pioneers failed."},{"time":205000,"text":"And there was something fundamental"},{"time":207000,"text":"that they were missing."},{"time":209000,"text":"They were missing the vision."},{"time":211000,"text":"It wasn't until the invention of the MR"},{"time":214000,"text":"and really the integration of MR"},{"time":216000,"text":"with focused ultrasound"},{"time":218000,"text":"that we could get the feedback --"},{"time":221000,"text":"both the anatomical and the physiological"},{"time":224000,"text":"in order to have a completely noninvasive, closed-loop"},{"time":228000,"text":"surgical procedure."}]},{"cues":[{"time":231000,"text":"So this is how it looks, you know,"},{"time":233000,"text":"the operating room of the future today."},{"time":236000,"text":"This is an MR suite with a focused ultrasound system."},{"time":239000,"text":"And I will give you several examples."},{"time":241000,"text":"So the first one is in the brain."},{"time":243000,"text":"One of the neurological conditions"},{"time":246000,"text":"that can be treated with focused ultrasound"},{"time":248000,"text":"are movement disorders,"},{"time":250000,"text":"like Parkinson's or essential tremor."},{"time":253000,"text":"What is typical to those conditions,"},{"time":256000,"text":"to essential tremor for example,"},{"time":259000,"text":"is inability"},{"time":262000,"text":"to drink or eat cereal or soup"},{"time":266000,"text":"without spilling everything all over you,"},{"time":269000,"text":"or write legibly so people can understand it,"},{"time":272000,"text":"and be really independent in your life"},{"time":275000,"text":"without the help of others."}]},{"cues":[{"time":277000,"text":"So I'd like you to meet John."},{"time":280000,"text":"John is a retired professor of history"},{"time":282000,"text":"from Virginia."},{"time":284000,"text":"So he suffered from essential tremor for many years."},{"time":287000,"text":"And medication didn't help him anymore."},{"time":291000,"text":"And many of those patients refused to undergo surgery"},{"time":294000,"text":"to have people cut into their brain."},{"time":296000,"text":"And about four or five months ago,"},{"time":299000,"text":"he underwent an experimental procedure."},{"time":304000,"text":"It is approved under an FDAIDE"},{"time":307000,"text":"at the University of Virginia"},{"time":309000,"text":"in Charlottesville"},{"time":311000,"text":"using focused ultrasound"},{"time":313000,"text":"to ablate a point in his thalamus."},{"time":318000,"text":"And this is his handwriting."},{"time":321000,"text":"\"On June 20th,\" if you can read it,"},{"time":324000,"text":"\"2011.\""},{"time":327000,"text":"This is his handwriting"},{"time":329000,"text":"on the morning of the treatment"},{"time":331000,"text":"before going into the MR"},{"time":333000,"text":"So now I'll take you through"},{"time":335000,"text":"[what] a typical procedure like that looks like,"},{"time":338000,"text":"[what] noninvasive surgery looks like."}]},{"cues":[{"time":341000,"text":"So we put the patient on the MR table."},{"time":344000,"text":"We attach a transducer, in this case, to the brain,"},{"time":346000,"text":"but if it will be a different organ,"},{"time":348000,"text":"it will be a different transducer attached to the patient."},{"time":352000,"text":"And the physician"},{"time":354000,"text":"will then take a regular MR scan."},{"time":357000,"text":"And the objective of that?"},{"time":359000,"text":"I don't have a pointer here,"},{"time":361000,"text":"but you see the green, sort of rectangle or trapezoid?"},{"time":366000,"text":"This is the sort of general area of the treatment."},{"time":368000,"text":"It's a safety boundary"},{"time":370000,"text":"around the target."},{"time":372000,"text":"It's a target in the thalamus."},{"time":374000,"text":"So once those pictures are acquired"},{"time":376000,"text":"and the physician has drawn"},{"time":379000,"text":"all the necessary safety limits and so on,"},{"time":382000,"text":"he selects basically a point --"},{"time":384000,"text":"you see the round point in the middle where the cursor is --"},{"time":387000,"text":"and he presses this blue button called \"sonicate.\""},{"time":390000,"text":"We call this instance of injecting the energy,"},{"time":393000,"text":"we call it sonication."},{"time":395000,"text":"The only handwork the physician does here"},{"time":398000,"text":"is moving a mouse."},{"time":400000,"text":"This is the only device he needs in this treatment."}]},{"cues":[{"time":403000,"text":"So he presses \"sonicate,\" and this is what happens."},{"time":406000,"text":"You see the transducer, the light blue."},{"time":408000,"text":"There's water in between the skull and the transducer."},{"time":411000,"text":"And it does this burst of energy."},{"time":413000,"text":"It elevates the temperature."},{"time":415000,"text":"We first need to verify"},{"time":417000,"text":"that we are on target."},{"time":419000,"text":"So the first sonication"},{"time":421000,"text":"is at lower energy."},{"time":423000,"text":"It doesn't do any damage,"},{"time":425000,"text":"but it elevates the temperature"},{"time":427000,"text":"by a few degrees."},{"time":429000,"text":"And one of the unique capabilities"},{"time":431000,"text":"that we leverage with the MR"},{"time":433000,"text":"is the ability to measure temperature noninvasively."},{"time":437000,"text":"This is really a unique capability of the MR."},{"time":440000,"text":"It is not being used"},{"time":442000,"text":"in regular diagnostic imaging."},{"time":444000,"text":"But here we can get"},{"time":446000,"text":"both the anatomical imaging and the temperature maps in real time."},{"time":449000,"text":"And you can see the points there on the graph."},{"time":452000,"text":"The temperature was raised"},{"time":454000,"text":"to 43 degrees C temporarily."},{"time":456000,"text":"This doesn't cause any damage."},{"time":458000,"text":"But the point is we are right on target."},{"time":460000,"text":"So once the physician verifies"},{"time":463000,"text":"that the focus spot is on the target he has chosen,"},{"time":466000,"text":"then we move to perform"},{"time":469000,"text":"a full-energy ablation"},{"time":471000,"text":"like you see here."},{"time":473000,"text":"And you see the temperature rises"},{"time":476000,"text":"to like 55 to 60 degrees C."},{"time":478000,"text":"If you do it for more than a second,"},{"time":480000,"text":"it's enough to basically destroy"},{"time":483000,"text":"the proteins of the cells."}]},{"cues":[{"time":487000,"text":"This is the outcome from a patient perspective --"},{"time":489000,"text":"same day after the treatment."},{"time":492000,"text":"This is an immediate relief."},{"time":494000,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":499000,"text":"Thank you."},{"time":501000,"text":"John is one of [about] a dozen"},{"time":504000,"text":"very heroic, courageous people"},{"time":508000,"text":"who volunteered for the study."},{"time":510000,"text":"And you have to understand"},{"time":512000,"text":"what is in people's mind"},{"time":514000,"text":"when they are willing to take the risk."},{"time":517000,"text":"And this is a quote from John after he wrote it."},{"time":520000,"text":"He said, \"Miraculous.\""},{"time":522000,"text":"And his wife said, \"This is the happiest moment of my life.\""},{"time":526000,"text":"And you wonder why."},{"time":528000,"text":"I mean, one of the messages I like to carry over"},{"time":531000,"text":"is, what about defending quality of life?"},{"time":534000,"text":"I mean, those people lose their independence."},{"time":536000,"text":"They are dependent on others."},{"time":538000,"text":"And John today is fully independent."},{"time":541000,"text":"He returned to a normal life routine."},{"time":544000,"text":"And he also plays golf,"},{"time":546000,"text":"like you do in Virginia"},{"time":548000,"text":"when you are retired."},{"time":553000,"text":"Okay, so you can see here the spot."},{"time":557000,"text":"It's like three millimeters in the middle of the brain."},{"time":559000,"text":"There's no damage outside."},{"time":561000,"text":"He suffers from no neurodeficit."},{"time":564000,"text":"There's no recovery needed, no nothing."},{"time":567000,"text":"He's back to his normal life."}]},{"cues":[{"time":569000,"text":"Let's move now"},{"time":571000,"text":"to a more painful subject."},{"time":573000,"text":"Pain is something"},{"time":575000,"text":"that can make your life miserable."},{"time":577000,"text":"And people are suffering from all kinds of pain"},{"time":579000,"text":"like neuropathic pain, lower-back pain"},{"time":583000,"text":"and cancer pain from bone metastases,"},{"time":586000,"text":"when the metastases get to your bones,"},{"time":589000,"text":"sometimes they are very painful."},{"time":592000,"text":"All those I've indicated"},{"time":594000,"text":"have already been shown"},{"time":596000,"text":"to be successfully treated"},{"time":598000,"text":"by focused ultrasound"},{"time":601000,"text":"relieving the pain, again, very fast."},{"time":604000,"text":"And I would like to tell you"},{"time":606000,"text":"about PJ."},{"time":610000,"text":"He's a 78 year-old farmer"},{"time":614000,"text":"who suffered from -- how should I say it? --"},{"time":617000,"text":"it's called pain in the butt."},{"time":619000,"text":"He had metastases in his right buttock,"},{"time":622000,"text":"and he couldn't sit"},{"time":624000,"text":"even with medication."},{"time":626000,"text":"He had to forgo all the farm activities."},{"time":633000,"text":"He was treated with radiation therapy,"},{"time":635000,"text":"state-of-the-art radiation therapy,"},{"time":637000,"text":"but it didn't help."},{"time":639000,"text":"Many patients like that favor radiation therapy."}]},{"cues":[{"time":642000,"text":"And again, he volunteered"},{"time":644000,"text":"to a pivotal study"},{"time":646000,"text":"that we ran worldwide,"},{"time":649000,"text":"also in the U.S."},{"time":653000,"text":"And his wife actually took him."},{"time":656000,"text":"They drove like three hours"},{"time":658000,"text":"from their farm to the hospital."},{"time":661000,"text":"He had to sit on a cushion,"},{"time":664000,"text":"stand still, not move,"},{"time":666000,"text":"because it was very painful."},{"time":669000,"text":"He took the treatment,"},{"time":671000,"text":"and on the way back,"},{"time":674000,"text":"he drove the truck by himself."},{"time":678000,"text":"So again, this is an immediate relief."},{"time":681000,"text":"And you have to understand"},{"time":683000,"text":"what those people feel"},{"time":685000,"text":"and what their family experiences"},{"time":688000,"text":"when it happens."},{"time":690000,"text":"He returned again"},{"time":692000,"text":"to his daily routine on the farm."},{"time":694000,"text":"He rides his tractor."},{"time":696000,"text":"He rides his horse to their mountain cabin regularly."},{"time":700000,"text":"And he has been very happy."}]},{"cues":[{"time":703000,"text":"But now, you ask me,"},{"time":706000,"text":"but what about war, the war on cancer?"},{"time":708000,"text":"Show us some primary cancer."},{"time":711000,"text":"What can be done there?"},{"time":713000,"text":"So I have good news and bad news."},{"time":715000,"text":"The good news: there's a lot that can be done."},{"time":718000,"text":"And it has been shown actually outside of the U.S."},{"time":721000,"text":"And doing that in the U.S."},{"time":725000,"text":"is very painful."},{"time":727000,"text":"I don't see, without this nation"},{"time":731000,"text":"taking it as some collective will"},{"time":735000,"text":"or something that is a national goal to make that happen,"},{"time":738000,"text":"it will not happen."},{"time":740000,"text":"And it's not just because of regulation;"},{"time":742000,"text":"it's because of the amount of money needed"},{"time":745000,"text":"under the current evidence-based medicine"},{"time":749000,"text":"and the size of trials and so on"},{"time":751000,"text":"to make it happen."}]},{"cues":[{"time":753000,"text":"So the first two applications"},{"time":755000,"text":"are breast cancer and prostate cancer."},{"time":758000,"text":"They were the first to be treated by focused ultrasound."},{"time":761000,"text":"And we have better-than-surgery results in breasts."},{"time":766000,"text":"But I have a message for the men here."},{"time":768000,"text":"We heard here yesterday Quyen"},{"time":771000,"text":"talking about the adverse event trait"},{"time":774000,"text":"in prostate cancer."},{"time":776000,"text":"There is a unique opportunity now"},{"time":778000,"text":"with focused ultrasound guided by MR,"},{"time":781000,"text":"because we can actually think about"},{"time":784000,"text":"prostate lumpectomy --"},{"time":786000,"text":"treating just the focal lesion"},{"time":788000,"text":"and not removing the whole gland,"},{"time":790000,"text":"and by that, avoiding all the issues"},{"time":793000,"text":"with potency and incontinence."},{"time":797000,"text":"Well, there are other cancer tumors in the abdomen --"},{"time":803000,"text":"quite lethal, very lethal actually --"},{"time":805000,"text":"pancreas, liver, kidney."},{"time":808000,"text":"The challenge there"},{"time":810000,"text":"with a breathing and awake patient --"},{"time":813000,"text":"and in all our treatments,"},{"time":815000,"text":"the patient is awake and conscious"},{"time":817000,"text":"and speaks with the physician --"},{"time":821000,"text":"is you have to teach the MR some tricks"},{"time":824000,"text":"how to do it in real time."},{"time":827000,"text":"And this will take time."},{"time":829000,"text":"This will take two years."}]},{"cues":[{"time":831000,"text":"But I have now a message to the ladies."},{"time":834000,"text":"And this is, in 2004,"},{"time":837000,"text":"the FDA has approved MR-guided focused ultrasounds"},{"time":840000,"text":"for the treatment of symptomatic uterine fibroids."},{"time":845000,"text":"Women suffer from that disease."},{"time":849000,"text":"All those tumors"},{"time":851000,"text":"have heavy bleeding during periods,"},{"time":853000,"text":"abdominal pressure, back pain,"},{"time":855000,"text":"frequent urination."},{"time":857000,"text":"And sometimes, they cannot even conceive and become pregnant"},{"time":861000,"text":"because of the fibroid."},{"time":863000,"text":"This is Frances."},{"time":865000,"text":"She was diagnosed with a grapefruit-sized fibroid."},{"time":867000,"text":"This is a big fibroid."},{"time":869000,"text":"She was offered a hysterectomy,"},{"time":871000,"text":"but this is an inconceivable proposition"},{"time":873000,"text":"for someone who wants to keep her pregnancy option."},{"time":876000,"text":"So she elected to undergo a focused ultrasound procedure"},{"time":880000,"text":"in 2008."},{"time":882000,"text":"And in 2010, she became a first-time mother to a healthy baby."},{"time":886000,"text":"So new life was born."}]},{"cues":[{"time":888000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":890000,"text":"So in conclusion,"},{"time":893000,"text":"I'd like to leave you with actually four messages."},{"time":896000,"text":"One is, think about the amount"},{"time":898000,"text":"of suffering that is saved"},{"time":900000,"text":"from patients undergoing noninvasive surgery,"},{"time":904000,"text":"and also the economical and emotional burden"},{"time":908000,"text":"removed from their families and communities"},{"time":911000,"text":"and the society at large --"},{"time":915000,"text":"and I think also from their physicians, by the way."},{"time":921000,"text":"And the other thing I would like you to think about"},{"time":924000,"text":"is the new type of relationship"},{"time":927000,"text":"between physician and patients"},{"time":929000,"text":"when you have a patient on the table"},{"time":932000,"text":"[who] is awake and can even monitor the treatment."},{"time":935000,"text":"In all our treatments,"},{"time":937000,"text":"the patient holds a stop sonication button."},{"time":939000,"text":"He can stop the surgery at any moment."}]},{"cues":[{"time":943000,"text":"And with that note,"},{"time":946000,"text":"I would like to thank you for listening."}]},{"cues":[{"time":949000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}